(146, 1, '2018-10-17 14:43:20', '2018-10-17 12:43:20', 'Defer parsing of JavaScript In order to load a page, the browser must parse the contents of all tags, which adds additional time to the page load. By minimizing the amount of JavaScript needed to render the page, and deferring parsing of unneeded JavaScript until it needs to be executed, you can reduce the initial load time of your page. How does your site score on this recommendation?', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '146', '', '', '2018-11-05 13:18:18', '2018-11-05 11:18:18', '', 8, 'http://127.0.0.1/rental-center/?p=146', 7, 'nav_menu_item', '', 0),
