(203, 1, '2018-10-21 09:40:11', '2018-10-21 07:40:11', 'I try to clone using SSH on a different Windows partition ( from the one I have SO installed and the SSH keys) and I getError: Please make sure you have the correct access rights\r\nand the repository exists.\r\n\r\nFix:\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>eval <code>ssh-agent</code></li>\r\n 	<li>ssh-add ~/.ssh/your ssh key</li>\r\n 	<li>enter you ssh key pwd</li>\r\n 	<li>run any git command you want</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Error: Please make sure you have the correct access rights and the repository exists.', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'error-please-make-sure-you-have-the-correct-access-rights-and-the-repository-exists', '', '', '2018-10-21 11:16:16', '2018-10-21 09:16:16', '', 0, 'http://127.0.0.1/rental-center/?p=203', 0, 'post', '', 0),
